jp.co.axa.apidemo.model

クラス Response<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.co.axa.apidemo.model.Response<T>
  • 型パラメータ:
    T - response type of data

    public class Response<T>
extends Object
    Immutable generic custom controller response model. This is the object being returned as body for every response. Having a consistant data structure throughout all your endpoint response makes it easier to use for clients in my experience.
